            "title": "美國聯邦調查局稱達拉斯移民和海關執法局槍擊系有針對性的暴力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"671\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dNpw.U2CzgyJnBNSnggaJA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY3MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/60bc19e0cf7d139eab7062a60344cabb\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 達拉斯移民和海關執法局(<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:ICE;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/ICE\">ICE</a>)發生槍擊事件，導致包括槍手在內的兩人死亡，聯邦執法官員稱這是針對該聯邦機構「有針對性的暴力行為」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯邦調查局達拉斯外勤辦公室負責人特工Joe Rothrock周三在發布會上表示，在槍手附近發現的彈藥似乎有反ICE字樣。官員們表示，另有數人受傷，但均非執法人員。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次襲擊是近幾個月來達拉斯地區ICE設施發生的第二起襲擊事件。ICE代理局長Todd Lyons表示，7月4日，德克薩斯州阿爾瓦拉多附近一處ICE的官員遭伏擊。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-21ed808c-d21d-33f2-ab90-de94f3ab23d2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"671\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nlH8jq.3HVUmutfHfXK4Qg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY3MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f0a19f5f50357be52783865a83509468\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">官員拒絕透露受害者身份，不過國土安全部長克里斯蒂·諾姆稱槍手自殺身亡。國土安全部此前表示，三人身亡。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">達拉斯警方表示，警員於上午6點40分左右接報趕到現場，並稱案件正在調查中。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「初步調查顯示，一名嫌疑人從一棟相鄰建築向政府大樓開槍，」警方在聲明中稱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Deadly Shooting at Dallas ICE Center Was ‘Targeted,’ FBI Says</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Julie Fine、Alexander Pearson.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(更新全文，新增詳情)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%94%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%92%8C%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E5%B1%80%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%A7%8D%E6%93%8A%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-%E8%87%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-131046161.html",
